com.absio.database.table

Class PublicKeys

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.absio.database.table.AbstractTable
      • com.absio.database.table.PublicKeys

  • public class PublicKeys
extends AbstractTable
    This class represents the PublicKeys table. It has the logic for producing all relevant SQL for inserting, updating deleting and reading from the table.
